<subSubSection pageId="7" pageNumber="32" type="comments">
<paragraph pageId="7" pageNumber="32">Comments.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="7" pageNumber="32">
This species is very similar to 
<taxonomicName genus="P." lsidName="P. amens" pageId="7" pageNumber="32" rank="species" species="amens">P. amens</taxonomicName>
in general appearance. However, it is distinguished from the latter by the following characters: head and antennal segments 
<normalizedToken originalValue="I–II">I-II</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken originalValue="V–VIII">V-VIII</normalizedToken>
brown, rest of body yellow (Fig. 15-16); postocular setae shorter than eyes, cheeks straight and weakly constricted behind eyes.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
